{"tid":1765930,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本首位神盾艦女艦長 大谷三穗大佐接掌二代妙高號","createTime":"2019-12-02T08:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T08:40:00.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d60e7ae9e531870cb66f52a91a10ed786639de","tid":1765930,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20191202/2332x1744_051115359200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20191202%2F2332x1744_051115359200.jpg&h=54acda1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20191202/1436x2096_766731095064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20191202%2F1436x2096_766731095064.jpg&h=c47e5c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本海上自衛隊今天誕生第一位神盾艦女艦長，由48歲一等海佐（大佐）大谷三穗接任妙高號驅逐艦（舷號DDG-175）艦長，肩負攔截彈道飛彈重任。<br />\n<br />\n日本共同社報導，妙高號驅逐艦母港在舞鶴基地（京都府舞鶴市），大谷三穗身為日本首位神盾艦女艦長，今天登上妙高號驅逐艦訓勉官士兵，「要毫不遲疑地執行本分工作」。<br />\n<br />\n妙高號驅逐艦乘員約300人，標準排水量約7250公噸、滿載排水量約9485公噸，是日本攔截彈道飛彈的骨幹之一。<br />\n<br />\n大谷接受媒體採訪時說，身為第一位女性艦長深感光榮。<br />\n<br />\n海上自衛隊表示，大谷出身大阪府吹田市，1996年以第一期女性學生畢業於防衛大學，並於2013年擔任首位練習艦的女艦長。<br />\n<br />\n日本朝日新聞指出，誕生第一位女艦長的妙高號，在日本海負責警戒北韓彈道飛彈的任務。大谷談到驅逐艦任務時說，雖然理解任務艱鉅，但心中沒有不安，將全力完成交付任務。<br />\n<br />\n日本產經新聞報導，大谷表示，感謝防衛省致力打造讓女性活躍的環境，並讓她肩負部分重責大任。"},{"pid":"89ff7d4c47d2bc5b0b0e14bda74164b8d63713c8","tid":1765930,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831aefa9d00fbb3fc4c49572a8850d50d3e888b0","tid":1765930,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:27:13.000Z","msg":"個樣幾後生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a346d7b5ac5f91bca9940e6761c00e33555726","tid":1765930,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國2.0萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8b55e9b03f3600a39683e46c16fdcb39cecc3a","tid":1765930,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"睇錯神盾局"},{"pid":"44f0fb99a20fcbb2efee62060d3707b0b99bb1ea","tid":1765930,"uid":267937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"351be5d0d1d176285f784321380a5c726a20ff83","tid":1765930,"uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08McRLN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08McRLN.jpg&h=7db8feb0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那女匪官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9110d0b42ec77d1d89ef23197e3f30166a461d","tid":1765930,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201508/e2812896baf32e4aff50921f7229de4c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201508%2Fe2812896baf32e4aff50921f7229de4c.JPG&h=27a5ecf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6240447eefbe34821b9c5b0c12dd60ab93c8e594","tid":1765930,"uid":15055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"支持架妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5219eadfd9510530ec981d3ebbe42b195b6fb3","tid":1765930,"uid":39365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會係大谷吉繼後代?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa